To mess around with ip 
$ sudo ip addr add 192.168.0.70/24 dev enp0s3 
-To change ip and also remember dev name can defer and depend on ones situation

Use del to delete connection
$ sudo ip addr del 192.168.0.70/24  dev enp0s3

To set ip to parrticular connection
- First add ip how described above then turn down connection and get it back up
$ sudo ip link set ensp03 down

- Up the connection
$ sudo ip link set ensp03 up

